      "title": "Logarithmically complete monotonicity of a function related to the Catalan-Qi function",
      "abstract": "Abstract In the paper, the authors find necessary and sufficient conditions such that a function related to the Catalan-Qi function, which is an alternative generalization of the Catalan numbers, is logarithmically complete monotonic."
